# Smart City Complaint Analytics — Power BI Dashboard

## 1. Problem Statement
City authorities receive 50,000+ citizen complaints across 7 categories (Garbage Collection,
Water Supply, Road Damage, Street Light Failure, Traffic Congestion, Drainage Problem, Public
Safety) and 8 zones. Manually tracking these is difficult as the city grows. This Power BI
dashboard gives city leadership a single view of complaint volume, resolution efficiency, and
geographic hotspots to support data-driven decisions.

## 2. Dataset Description
- **Source:** `smart_city_complaints_50k.csv`
- **Rows:** 50,000 complaints
- **Zones:** 8 (Central, East, Industrial, North, North-East, South, South-West, West)
- **Categories:** 7
- **Key fields used:** Complaint_ID, Complaint_Date, Zone, Category, Department, Status,
  Priority, Resolution_Delay_Days, Citizen_Satisfaction_Score

